|----------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| **Arbitrage Opportunity**        | Mint and sell stablecoins for profit            | Buy stablecoins to earn interest and sell later   |
| **Funding Mechanism**            | Mark - Index = Mark - 1                         | Mark - Index = Mark - 1                          |
