| **Power $p$**                | 0.5                      |
| **Index Asset**               | ETH                      |
| **Collateral Asset**          | USD                      |
| **Numeraire**                 | USD                      |
| **Payoff**                    | $V = 2 \times (k \times (\text{eth price}))^{0.5}$ |
