	(446, 56, '### Can you explain the ETH Power Perpetual?

The ETH power perp has a payoff based on the square of ETH''s price. Under Black-Scholes assumptions, its price is given by:

$$
S^2 \frac{1}{2e^{-f(r + v^2)} - 1}
$$

